#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:4
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introducció"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:6
msgid ""
"After starting Blender and closing the :ref:`Splash Screen <splash>` your "
"Blender window should look something similar to the image below. Blender's "
"user interface is consistent across all platforms."
msgstr ""
"Després de començar Blender i tancar la :ref:`Pantalla Inicial <splash>` la "
"finestra del Blender hauria de ser semblant a la imatge següent. La "
"interfície d'usuari de Blender és consistent a totes les plataformes."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:13
msgid "The default startup Blender window."
msgstr "La finestra per defecte d'inici de Blender"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:17
msgid "Interface Elements"
msgstr "Elements de la interfície"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:23
msgid ""
"The interface can be customized to match specific tasks using :doc:`Screen "
"Layouts </interface/window_system/screens>`, which can then be named and "
"saved for later use. The default screen is described below."
msgstr ""
"La interfície es pot personalitzar per a que coincideixi amb tasques "
"específiques utilitzant :doc:`Disposicions de Pantalla </interface/"
"window_system/screens>`, que es poden anomenar i desar per a un ús "
"posterior. La pantalla predeterminada es descriu a continuació."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:27
msgid ""
"A screen is organized into one or more :doc:`Areas </interface/window_system/"
"areas>` with each area containing an *Editor*."
msgstr ""
"Una pantalla està organitzada en una o més :doc:`Àrees </interface/"
"window_system/areas>` amb cada àrea tinguent un *Editor*."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:32
msgid "The Default Screen"
msgstr "La pantalla per defecte"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:34
msgid ""
"By default Blender starts up showing the default screen, which is separated "
"into five areas containing the Editors listed below:"
msgstr ""
"De manera predeterminada Blender s'inicia amb la pantalla predeterminada, "
"que està separada en cinc àrees que contenen els Editors que es detallen a "
"continuació:"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:37
msgid "The Info Editor at the top."
msgstr "L'Editor d'informació a la part superior."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:38
msgid "A large 3D View."
msgstr "Una amplia vista 3D."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:39
msgid "A Timeline at the bottom."
msgstr "Una línia de temps a la part inferior."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:40
msgid "An Outliner at the top right."
msgstr "Un Organitzador a la part superior dreta."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:41
msgid "A Properties Editor at the bottom right."
msgstr "Un editor de propietats a la part inferior dreta."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:45
msgid "Blender's default Screen Layout with five Editors."
msgstr "Disposició de pantalla predeterminat de Blender amb cinc editors."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:47
msgid "Info (1), 3D View (2), Outliner (3), Properties (4) and Timeline (5)."
msgstr ""
"Informació (1), Vista 3D (2), Organitzador (3), Propietats (4) and Linea de "
"Temps (5)."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:51
msgid "Components of an Editor"
msgstr "Components d'un Editor"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:53
msgid ""
"In general an editor provides a way to view and modify your work through a "
"specific part of Blender. Editors are divided into :doc:`/interface/"
"window_system/regions`. Regions can have smaller structuring elements like :"
"doc:`tabs and panels </interface/window_system/tabs_panels>` with buttons, "
"controls and widgets placed within them."
msgstr ""
"En general, un editor proporciona una manera de veure i modificar el vostre "
"treball a través d'una part específica de Blender. Els editors es divideixen "
"en :doc:`/interface/window_system/regions`. Les regions poden tenir elements "
"més petits com ara :doc:`Pestanyes i Panels</interface/window_system/"
"tabs_panels>` amb botons, controls i widgets col·locats dins d'ells."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:62
msgid "The 3D View editor."
msgstr "L'Editor de Vista en 3D"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:64
msgid ""
"Yellow: Main Region, green: Header, blue: Tool Shelf, purple: Operator "
"Panel, red: Properties Region."
msgstr ""
"Groc: Regió principal, verd: Capçalera, blau: Taula d'eines, violeta: Panell "
"de l'Operador, vermell: Propietats de la Regió."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:69
msgid "User Interface Principles"
msgstr "Principis de la interfície d'usuari"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:73
msgid "Non Overlapping"
msgstr "No superposició"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:72
msgid ""
"The UI is designed to allow you to view all relevant options and tools at a "
"glance without pushing or dragging editors around."
msgstr ""
"La interfície d'usuari està dissenyada per permetre veure totes les opcions "
"i eines rellevants d'una ullada sense pressionar ni arrossegar els editors."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:78
msgid "Non Blocking"
msgstr "No bloqueig"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:76
msgid ""
"Tools and interface options do not block the user from any other parts of "
"Blender. Blender typically does not use pop-up boxes (requiring users to "
"fill in data before running an operation)."
msgstr ""
"Les eines i les opcions d'interfície no bloquegen l'usuari de cap altra part "
"de Blender. Blender normalment no utilitza finestres emergents (requereix "
"que els usuaris omplin dades abans d'executar una operació)."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:83
msgid "Non Modal Tools"
msgstr "Eines no modals"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:81
msgid ""
"Tools can be accessed efficiently without taking time to select between "
"different tools. Many tools use consistent and predictable, mouse and "
"keyboard actions for interaction."
msgstr ""
"Es pot accedir de manera eficient a les eines sense utilizar el temps per "
"seleccionar entre diferents eines. Moltes eines utilitzen accions coherents "
"i previsibles, de ratolí i teclat per a la interacció."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:86
msgid "Customization"
msgstr "Personalització"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:88
msgid ""
"Blender also makes heavy use of keyboard shortcuts to speed up work. These "
"can also be customized in the :ref:`Keymap Editor <prefs-input-keymap-"
"editor>`."
msgstr ""
"Blender també fa un ús intensiu de les dreceres de teclat per accelerar el "
"treball. També es poden personalitzar en :ref:`Editor de dreceres de Teclat "
"<prefs-input-keymap-editor>`."

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:93
msgid "Theme colors"
msgstr "Tema de colors"

#: ../../manual/interface/window_system/introduction.rst:94
msgid ""
"Blender allows for most of its interface color settings to be changed to "
"suit the needs of the user. If you find that the colors you see on screen do "
"not match those mentioned in the Manual then it could be that your default "
"theme has been altered. Creating a new theme or selecting/altering a pre-"
"existing one can be done by selecting the :doc:`User Preferences </"
"preferences/index>` editor and clicking on the *Themes* tab."
msgstr ""
"Blender permet canviar la major part de la configuració del color de la "
"interfície per adaptar-se a les necessitats de l'usuari. Si trobeu que els "
"colors que veieu a la pantalla no coincideixen amb els esmentats en el "
"manual, podria ser que s'hagi modificat el tema predeterminat. Es pot crear "
"un nou tema o seleccionar/modificar un preexistent si seleccioneu l'editor "
"a :doc:`Preferencies d'Usuari </preferences/index>` i fent clic a la "
"pestanya *Temes*."
